      "title_at_amendment": "Throttle controls.",
      "text": "(a) There must be a separate throttle control for each engine. (b) Throttle controls must be arranged to allow-- (1) Separate control of each engine; and (2) Simultaneous control of all engines. (c) Each throttle control must give a positive and immediate responsive means of controlling its engine.",
